data.description: Welcome Home to this stunning property in Beasley Tx! Upon entry you are greeted by a home office with french doors. The living room is spacious & features high ceilings. The kitchen is a chef's dream with tons of cabinet/counter space. The primary suite is inviting with tons of natural light and overlooks the stunning back yard. The primary bath is complete with dual sinks, separate shower, soaker tub and walk in closet. Head upstairs to a game room & two secondary bedrooms. The backyard will have you in awe! Relax the day away in the gorgeous pool & spa, enjoy a cookout under the covered patio, This home is a dream!
